OL,3,CPolice Ombudsman returns to work
OL,5,FPolice Service of Northern Ireland
OL,6,Fofficers went to the property at about
OL,7,F6.30pm on Saturday September 23 2023,
OL,8,Fafter a report of a domestic incident.
OL,10,FA man was arrested as part of the
OL,11,Finquiry and later released pending a
OL,12,Freport to prosecutors.
OL,14,FA file was subsequently sent to the
OL,15,FPublic Prosecution Service (PPS) and a
OL,16,Fcaution issued to the man who had been
OL,17,Farrested.
OL,19,FWest Midlands Police were then tasked
OL,20,Fwith investigating further aspects of
OL,21,Fthe incident.
