OL,3,CPolice Ombudsman returns to work
OL,5,FIn June 2024, the Northern Ireland
OL,6,FAssembly was told that Mrs Anderson
OL,7,Fhad taken a leave of absence due to
OL,8,Fillness.
OL,10,FIn a statement on Monday, Mrs Anderson
OL,11,Fsaid: "I am pleased to be back at work
OL,12,Fand am looking forward to recommencing
OL,13,Fmy role.
