OL,5,F"I would like to thank my senior staff
OL,6,Fwho led the work of the office during
OL,7,Fmy illness and continued to
OL,8,Fdemonstrate the value of our
OL,9,Finvestigations in building public
OL,10,Fconfidence in independent
OL,11,Finvestigation of police complaints and
OL,12,Fin our work to improve policing."
OL,14,FIn relation into the incident in
OL,15,FSeptember 2023, a PSNI spokesman said:
OL,16,F"There is an ongoing police
OL,17,Finvestigation and it would be
OL,18,Finappropriate to comment at this time."
