OL,3,CPolice Ombudsman returns to work
OL,5,FA PPS spokesman said: "The PPS
OL,6,Fcarefully considered all the available
OL,7,Fevidence on a police investigation
OL,8,Ffile reporting one individual arrested
OL,9,Fin respect of an alleged domestic
OL,10,Fincident in Holywood, Co Down, in
OL,11,FSeptember 2023.
OL,13,F"Having applied the test for
OL,14,Fprosecution, it was determined that
OL,15,Fthe evidential test was met for the
OL,16,Foffence of common assault, and that,
OL,17,Fhaving regard to all the
OL,18,Fcircumstances, the matter could
OL,19,Fproperly be dealt with by way of a
OL,20,Fcaution.
