OL,3,CPolice Ombudsman returns to work
OL,5,F"The caution was accepted by the
OL,6,Freported individual in September 2024
OL,7,Fand administered by police.
OL,9,F"All parties were informed at the time.
OL,11,F"All PPS decision-making was carried
OL,12,Fout independently, impartially and in
OL,13,Fline with the PPS code for
OL,14,Fprosecutors."
OL,16,FA caution is a formal reprimand by
OL,17,Fpolice. While not a conviction, it is
OL,18,Frecorded on a person's criminal record
OL,19,Ffor a period of six years for an adult.
